nodes.text: The Sullustan Cargo Freighter, also known as the Sullustan Cargo Barge, was a model of freighter with Sullustan influence that was active during the war between the First Order and the Resistance. Many of these starships joined the citizens' fleet that was assembled by General Lando Calrissian to aid the Resistance against the forces of the Sith Eternal during the Battle of Exegol. It could hold cargo, had three engines, and was equipped with a hyperdrive.

The Sullustan Cargo Freighter was first seen in Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker and identified as such in the clip "A Final Alliance" behind the scenes featurette that comes with the Target exclusive of the home video.
